<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871207-0134 </DOCNO><HL> American Petrofina Purchase</HL><DD> 12/07/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> XCOL APIAPETROLEUM (PET)TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> DALLAS  </DATELINE><TEXT>   American Petrofina Inc. said its Fina Oil andamp; Chemical Co. unit completed its purchase of nearly all of Exploration Co. of Louisiana's producing oil and gas properties in Louisiana and certain other assets for about $79 million.    A spokesman for the energy exploration and production concern said the purchase increases American Petrofina's natural gas reserves about 25%. He wouldn't elaborate on the size of the reserves.    Exploration Co., based in Lafayette, La., is an oil and gas exploration and drilling company. </TEXT></DOC>